description:
This content adds two new pieces of content to the game:
1. A new model (costume) of the specialized songstress AI, #kzn-chan (Kizuna-chan)
2. An additional song: "DOGS ⌘HYNOME feat. #kzn"

*Models can be switched in both the Game Mode and the View Mode.
*Kizuna AI costumes cannot be used with #kzn's model.
*#kzn costumes cannot be used with Kizuna AI's model.
name: Kizuna AI - Touch the Beat! DLC Model (Costume) "#kzn" + Additional Song "DOGS ⌘HYNOME feat. #kzn"
